Technical Notes
	•	Reorder: check each variant against current CampaignItem availability before adding. Use the CURRENT campaign the buyer ordered from (campaign_id on Order). If campaign is ENDED, show "This campaign has ended — browse active campaigns."
	•	Cancellation eligibility: CONFIRMED + shipped_at IS NULL + created_at > now() - 1h. The 1-hour window is a platform policy choice — configurable as a future PlatformSettings field.
	•	Cancel API: POST /api/account/orders/[id]/cancel → verify session + ownership → stripe.refunds.create(stripe_charge_id) → Order.status=CANCELLED → logOrderEvent(ORDER_CANCELLED, BUYER) → sendEmail(order_cancelled, buyer)
