UX / Design Notes
	•	The "Reorder" button is one of the highest-value repeat-purchase features in the entire epic — make it prominent on delivered orders. Consider copy like "Buy this again for [Org Name]" to reinforce the cause.
	•	The cancellation modal must be cautious and clear — but not so alarming that buyers feel punished. Use neutral tone, clearly state the refund timeline.
